@Atc.LogAnalytics.Api.Sample_HostAddress = https://localhost:46712
@computer = mycomputer

### GetHeartbeats

GET {{Atc.LogAnalytics.Api.Sample_HostAddress}}/heartbeats
Accept: application/json

### GetHeartbeats with computer filter

GET {{Atc.LogAnalytics.Api.Sample_HostAddress}}/heartbeats?computer={{computer}}
Accept: application/json

###
